\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\sl300\slmult1\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11692121 {\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 16.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 He that keeps the commandments keeps his own soul; but he that despises his ways shall perish. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 17.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 He that has pity on the poor  lends to the Lord; and he will recompense to him according to his gift. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 18.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Chasten thy son, for so he shall be hopeful; and b
e not exalted  in thy soul to haughtiness. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 19.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  A malicious man shall be severely punished, and if he commit injury, he shall also lose his life. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 20.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Hear, son,  the instruction of thy father, that thou mayest be wise at thy latter end. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 21.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  There are many thoughts in a man's heart; but the counsel of the  Lord abides for ever. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 22.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 Mercy is a fruit to a man: and a poor man is better than a rich liar. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 23.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 The fear of the Lord is life to a man: and  he shall lodge without fear in places where knowledge is not seen. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 24.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 He that unjustly hides his hands in his bosom, will not even bring  them up to his mouth. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 25.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 When a pestilent character is scourged, a simple man is made wiser: and if thou reprove a wise man, he will  understand discretion.   
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs19\f35\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 \sect }\sectd 
\marglsxn1319\margrsxn1319\linex0\endnhere\sectdefaultcl\sectrsid8206889\sftnbj \pard\plain \s24\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\cs19\f35\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 Tuesday in the Sixth Week - At the Sixth Hour   
\par }\pard\plain \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f2\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Troparion of the Prophecy, in the 5th Tone: 
\par An invincible wall hast Thou given to our city, the Virgin who bore Thee; through her, O Savior, do Thou rescue our souls from the evils that surround us, we pray.
\par 
\par }{\cs27\b\i\f1\fs24\cf15\insrsid3042872 Choir:}{\cs18\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid3042872  Glory\'85. Both Now\'85}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 And the choir repeats the Troparion
\par 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Prokeimenon, Psalm 108, in the 4}{\cs19\f35\fs32\super\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 th}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Tone:}{
\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 Help me, O Lord my God, and save me according to Thy mercy.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  O God, my praise do not pass over in silence.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\pararsid16721749 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs21\b\fs36\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511 Deacon:}{\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511  
