 And the Lord said to Jacob, Return to the land of thy father, and to thy family, and I will be with thee. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 4.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 And Jacob sent and called Lea  and Rachel to the plain where the flocks were. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 5.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  And he said to them, I see the face of your father, that it is no
t toward me as before but  the God of my father was with me. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 6.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  And ye too know that with all my might I have served your father. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 7.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  But your father deceived me,  and changed my wages for the ten lambs, yet God gave him lion power to hurt me. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 8.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  If lie should say thus, The speckled shall be thy  reward, then the cattle would bear speckled; and if he should say The white shall be thy reward, then would all the cattle bear white. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 9.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  So  God has taken away all the cattle of your father, and given them to me. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 10.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 And it came to pass when the cattle conceived and were with  young that beheld with mine eyes in sleep, and behold the he-goats and the rams leaping on the sheep and the she-goats, speckled and  variegated and spotted with ash-coloured spots. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 11.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   And the angel of God said to me in a dream, Jacob; and I said, What is it? }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 12.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   And  he said, Look up with thine eyes, and behold the he-goats and the rams leaping on the sheep and the she-goats, speckled and variegated  and spotted with ash-coloured spots;  I 
have seen all things that Laban does to thee. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 13.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 I am God that appeared to thee in the place of  God, where thou anointedst a pillar to me, and vowedst to me there a vow; now then arise and depart out of this land, depart into the land  of thy nativity, and I will be with thee. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 14.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   And Rachel and Lea answered and said to him Have we yet a part of inheritance in the house  of our father? }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 15.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   Are we not considered strangers by him? for he has sold us, and quite devoured our money. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 16.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 All the wealth and the  glory which God has taken from our father, it shall be ours and our children's; now then do whatsoever God has said to thee.   
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 
