\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 He is merciful and compassionate and righteous.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Blessed is the man that feareth the Lord.
\par 
