\par Deal with us according to Thy mercy, O Lord, and deliver us not up with our sins, O holy Master Almighty, we pray Thee.
\par 
\par }{\cs27\b\i\f1\fs24\cf15\insrsid3042872 Choir:}{\cs18\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid3042872  Glory\'85. Both Now\'85}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 And the choir repeats the Troparion
\par 
