\par Forget not the voice of Thy servants, O Lord; remember that at all times we have placed our hope in Thee, O All-powerful One, and help us, we pray.
\par 
\par }{\cs27\b\i\f1\fs24\cf15\insrsid3042872 Choir:}{\cs18\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid3042872  Glory\'85. Both Now\'85}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121   }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 And the choir repeats the Troparion
\par 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Prokeimenon, Psalm 117, in the 4}{\cs19\f35\fs32\super\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 th}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Tone:}{
\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 This is the gate of the Lord, the righteous shall enter in thereat.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  O give thanks unto the Lord, for He is good, for His mercy endureth for ever.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\pararsid16721749 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs21\b\fs36\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511 Deacon:}{\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511  
