\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\sl300\slmult1\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11692121 {\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 8.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 Thus saith the Lord, As a grape stone shall be found in the cluster, and they shall say, Destroy it not; for a blessing is in it: so will I do  for the sake of him that serves me, for his sake I will not destroy [them] all. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 9.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  And I will lead forth the se
ed [that came] of Jacob and of  Juda, and they shall inherit my holy mountain: and mine elect and my servants shall inherit it, and shall dwell. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 10.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 And there shall be in the  forest folds of flocks, and the valley of Achor [shall] be for a resting place of herds for my people, who have sought me. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 11.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 But ye are  they that have left me, and forget my holy mountain, and prepare a table for the devil, and fill up the drink offering to Fortune. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 12.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 I will  deliver you up to the sword, ye shall all fall by slaughter: for I called you, and ye hearkened not; I spoke, and ye refused to hear; and ye  did evil in my sight, and chose the things wherein I delighted not. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 13.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Therefore thus saith the Lord, Behold, my servants shall eat, but ye  shall hunger: behold, my s
ervants shall drink, but ye shall thirst: behold my servants shall rejoice, but ye shall be ashamed. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 14.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 behold, my  servants shall exult with joy, but ye shall cry for the sorrow of your heart, and shall howl for the vexation of your spirit. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 15.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  For ye sh
all  leave your name for a loathing to my chosen, and the Lord shall destroy you: but my servants shall be called by a new name, }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 16.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 which  shall be blessed on the earth; for they shall bless the true God: and thy that swear upon the earth shall swear by the true God; for they shall  forget the former affliction, it shall not come into their mind.   
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Prokeimenon, Psalm 118, in the 4}{\cs19\f35\fs32\super\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 th}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Tone:}{
\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 The way of Thy commandments have I run, when Thou didst enlarge my heart.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Set before me for a law, O Lord, the way of Thy statutes.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs19\f35\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 \sect }\sectd 
