\cs19\f35\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 Thursday in the Sixth Week - At Vespers   
\par }\pard\plain \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f2\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Prokeimenon, Psalm 119, in the 6}{\cs19\f35\fs32\super\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 th}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Tone:}{
\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 Unto the Lord in mine affliction have I cried, and He heard me.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  O Lord, deliver my soul from unrighteous lips and from a crafty tongue.
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\pararsid16721749 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs21\b\fs36\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511 Deacon:}{\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511  
