\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  I have lifted up mine eyes to the mountains, from whence cometh my help.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872 
