\par 
\par }{\cs23\i\f1\fs24\insrsid3042872 Reader:}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The Prokeimenon, Psalm 121, in the 4}{\cs19\f35\fs32\super\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 th}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Tone:}{
\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872  
\par }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 Because of the house of the Lord our God, I have sought good things for thee.
\par 
\par }{\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid3042872 Stichos: }{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  I was glad because of them that said unto me: Let us go into the house of the Lord.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\pararsid16721749 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs21\b\fs36\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511 Deacon:}{\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid9070511  
