\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\sl300\slmult1\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11692121 {\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 8.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Open thy mouth with the word of God, and judge all fairly. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 9.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Open thy mouth and judge justly, and plead the cause of the poor and  weak. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 10.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Who shall find a virtuous woman? for such a one is more valuable than precious stones. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 11.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 The heart of her husband trusts in  her: such a one shall stand in no need of fine spoils. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 12.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  For she employs all her living for her husband's good. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 13.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Gathering wool and flax,  she makes it serviceable with her hands. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 14.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  She is like a ship trading from a distance: so she procures her livelihood. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 15.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 And she rises by  night, and gives food to her household, and appointed tasks to her maidens. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 16.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 She views a farm, and buys it: and with the fruit of her  hands she plants a possession. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 17.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  She strongly girds her loins, and strengthens her arms for work. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 18.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  And she finds by experience that  working is good; and her candle goes not out all night. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 19.}{
\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  She reaches forth her arms to needful works, and applies her hands to the  spindle. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 20.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  And she opens her ha
nds to the needy, and reaches out fruit to the poor.  }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 21.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 Her husband is not anxious about those at home  when he tarries anywhere abroad: for all her household are clothed. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 22.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 She makes for her husband clothes of double texture, and  garments for herself of fine linen and scarlet. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 23.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 And her husband becomes a distinguished person in the gates, when he sits in council with  the old inhabitants of the land. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 24.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 She makes fine linens, and sells girdles to the Chananites: she opens her mouth heedfully and with  propriety, and controls her tongue. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 25.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 She puts on strength and honour; and rejoices in the last days. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 26.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  The ways of her household are  careful, and she eats not the bread of idleness. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 27.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  But she opens her mouth wisely, and according to law. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 28.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  An
d her kindness to them  sets up her children for them, and they grow rich, and her husband praises her. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 29.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 Many daughters have obtained wealth, many have  wrought valiantly; but thou hast exceeded, thou hast surpassed all. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 30.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121  Charms are false, and woman'
s beauty is vain: for it is a wise  woman that is blessed, and let her praise the fear of the Lord. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 31.}{\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid3042872\charrsid11692121 
 Give her of the fruit of her lips; and let her husband be praised in the  gates. 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs19\f35\fs32\insrsid2621940 \sect }\sectd \marglsxn1319\margrsxn1319\linex0\endnhere\sectdefaultcl\sectrsid8206889\sftnbj 
